Paper: hep-th/9310005

Date: 1993-10-01

Title: Integrable Generalisations of the 2-dimensional Born Infeld Equation

Authors: D.B. Fairlie and J.A. Mulvey

Comments: 11 pages, Latex, DTP/93/39

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A27 (1994) 1317-1324

The Born-Infeld equation in two dimensions is generalised to higherdimensions whilst retaining Lorentz Invariance and complete integrability. Thisgeneralisation retains homogeneity in second derivatives of the field.